<p>In this case we use the posterior samples of the parameters to construct a trace plot and estimate the posterior distribution of <img src="https://web.archive.org/web/20250518100700im_/https://s0.wp.com/latex.php?latex=%5Calpha&amp;bg=ffffff&amp;fg=000000&amp;s=0" alt="\alpha" title="\alpha" class="latex"/>:</p>
<div class="chunk" id="results-CRPalpha2">
